  <h1>Thyroid Test</h1>
  <p>The thyroid test helps measure hormone levels to check the health of your thyroid gland.</p>
  
  <h2>Types of Tests</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>TSH (Thyroid Stimulating Hormone)</li>
    <li>T3 (Triiodothyronine)</li>
    <li>T4 (Thyroxine)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Preparation</h2>
  <p>No special preparation is usually needed. Follow your doctorâ€™s advice.</p>

  <h2>Importance</h2>
  <p>These tests help detect hypothyroidism, hyperthyroidism, and other thyroid disorders.</p>
